													SHARE
												</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_twitter shareCount"><a class="js-shareLinks" target="_blank" onclick="window.open('https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2020%2fapril%2fapologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html&via=CTMagazine&text=The+Moral+Order+of+the+World+Points+to+God&counturl=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2020%2fapril%2fapologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html&sharetext=The+Moral+Order+of+the+World+Points+to+God+via+%40CTMagazine', 'newwindow', 'width=500, height=350'); return false;" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2020%2fapril%2fapologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html&via=CTMagazine&text=The+Moral+Order+of+the+World+Points+to+God&counturl=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2020%2fapril%2fapologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html&sharetext=The+Moral+Order+of+the+World+Points+to+God+via+%40CTMagazine" title="Share on Twitter"><span>tweet</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_whatsapp"><a class="js-shareLinks" target="_blank" href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?text=https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2020/april/apologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html?utm_source%3dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3dwebshare%26utm_campaign%3dCT" title="Share on WhatsApp" data-provider="whatsapp"><span>Share</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_share"><a class="js-shareLink js-trackJanrainClick linkVar" href="https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2020/april/apologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html?share=" data-modalid="shareUrlModal" data-shareurl="https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2020/april/apologetics-moral-order-of-world-points-to-god.html?share=" data-eventaction="Unlock Article" title="Share link to this article" data-itemid="181101"><span>link</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_email"><a href="mailto:?to=&subject=Christianity Today: The Moral Order of the World Points t