<div class="read-these-next spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-20"><h2 class="heading-section-lg spacer-bottom-25">Read These Next</h2><ul class="row list-unstyled"><li class="col-t3 spacer-bottom-30 trending"><div class="bg-flag uppercase spacer-bottom-1">Trending</div>
<figure class="spacer-bottom-5"><a href="/ct/2020/march-web-only/covid-19-coronavirus-20-prayers-to-pray-during-pandemic.html" title="20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic" class="js-clickTrack archive-badge" data-type="article" data-id="181226" data-category="Article" data-action="Read These Next Related" data-label="20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic"><img src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/116063.jpg?w=220" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/116063.jpg?w=440 2x" width="220" alt="20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic" title="20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic" /></a></figure><div class="slug"><a class="js-clickTrack" data-category="" data-action="" data-label="Prayer" href="/ct/search?type=keyword&query=Prayer">
																	Prayer
																</a></div>
<a class="title  title-3 js-clickTrack  js-editableItem js-clickTrack" href="/ct/2020/march-web-only/covid-19-coronavirus-20-prayers-to-pray-during-pandemic.html" data-type="article" data-id="181226" data-category="Article" data-action="Read These Next Related" data-label="20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic">20 Prayers to Pray During This Pandemic</a><div class="deck spacer-top-5">As COVID-19 sends the globe into crisis, it also sends us to our knees.</div>
<div class="byline spacer-top-8">Jen Pollock Michel</div>
<span class="btn-espanol spacer-right-20 spacer-top-10"><a class="lang-switcher" href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/20-oraciones-por-covid-19-coronavirus-orar-pandemia-latin.html">
									Espa&ntilde;ol
								</a></span><span class="btn-espanol spacer-right-20 spacer-top-10"><a class="lang-switcher" href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/20-prieres-covid-19-coronavirus-prier-pandemie-francais.html">
									Fran&ccedil;ais
